<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>Activity Choice ✨</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fredoka:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>

*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:'Fredoka', sans-serif;
}

body{
    min-height:100vh;
    background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ffe4ec,#f5e8ff);
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    padding:20px;
}

.card{
    background:white;
    width:100%;
    max-width:650px;
    padding:40px;
    border-radius:32px;
    box-shadow:0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    text-align:center;
    animation:fadeIn .5s ease;
}

.header{
    font-size:2rem;
    line-height:1.3;
    margin-bottom:15px;
}

.subheader{
    color:#888;
    margin-bottom:35px;
}

.question{
    font-size:1.2rem;
    margin-bottom:25px;
}

.options{
    display:flex;
    flex-direction:column;
    gap:15px;
}

.option{
    background:#f7f0ff;
    border:none;
    border-radius:999px;
    padding:18px;
    font-size:1rem;
    cursor:pointer;
    transition:.25s;
}

.option:hover{
    transform:translateY(-3px);
    background:#ead8ff;
}

.footer{
    margin-top:25px;
    font-size:0.85rem;
    color:#999;
}

@keyframes fadeIn{
    from{
        opacity:0;
        transform:translateY(20px);
    }
    to{
        opacity:1;
        transform:translateY(0);
    }
}

</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="card">

    <h1 class="header">
        hehehe you big back
    </h1>

    <p class="subheader">
         now choose an activity that we should do
    </p>

    <div class="options">

        <button class="option"
            onclick="location.href='bonus-question.html'">
            🎳 Bowling
        </button>

        <button class="option"
            onclick="location.href='bonus-question.html'">
            🎲 Board Games / Game Room
        </button>

        <button class="option"
            onclick="location.href='bonus-question.html'">
            🐱 Cat / Dog Cafe
        </button>

        <button class="option"
            onclick="location.href='bonus-question.html'">
            ⛳ Mini Golf
        </button>

        <button class="option"
            onclick="location.href='bonus-question.html'">
            🌟Tufting
        </button>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        choose carefully... this determines how competitive i get 
    </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
